{"uid":"69f9cecb61dc8420","name":"[BUG-OT-004] TC-OT-012 — GET /actuator/health: Must return 200 UP (returns 504)","fullName":"oauth-token-spr-fetcher-api.spec.ts:621:7","historyId":"6af7dbeef552617a074cd35e709dcbe2:90c8e83f81eaf895bc56cf1f10012bbc","time":{"start":1783045114162,"stop":1783045174365,"duration":60203},"description":"**[KNOWN BUG — BUG-OT-004]**\n\n**What this test does:**\nCalls GET /oauth-token/actuator/health and verifies it returns 200 with body {\"status\":\"UP\"}.\n\n**Expected:** HTTP 200 with {\"status\":\"UP\"}\n**Actual:** HTTP 504 Gateway Timeout\n\n**Root Cause:** The APISIX gateway has no route configured for /oauth-token/actuator/*. The request never reaches the Spring Boot actuator endpoint.\n\n**Impact:** The following are all broken:\n1. Kubernetes liveness and readiness probes (causing unnecessary pod restarts or    marking the pod as not-ready)\n2. Uptime monitoring dashboards\n3. CI/CD pipeline health checks that gate deployments","descriptionHtml":"<p><strong>[KNOWN BUG — BUG-OT-004]</strong></p>\n<p><strong>What this test does:</strong><br />\nCalls GET /oauth-token/actuator/health and verifies it returns 200 with body {&quot;status&quot;:&quot;UP&quot;}.</p>\n<p><strong>Expected:</strong> HTTP 200 with {&quot;status&quot;:&quot;UP&quot;}<br />\n<strong>Actual:</strong> HTTP 504 Gateway Timeout</p>\n<p><strong>Root Cause:</strong> The APISIX gateway has no route configured for /oauth-token/actuator/*. The request never reaches the Spring Boot actuator endpoint.</p>\n<p><strong>Impact:</strong> The following are all broken:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Kubernetes liveness and readiness probes (causing unnecessary pod restarts or    marking the pod as not-ready)</li>\n<li>Uptime monitoring dashboards</li>\n<li>CI/CD pipeline health checks that gate deployments</li>\n</ol>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[],"testStage":{"descriptio